2026-05-14T05:00:39.8794655Z 20-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/build/intermediates/tmp/manifest/test/debug/tempFile2ProcessTestManifest2278297219259955775.xml:21:22-78
2026-05-14T05:00:39.8794812Z 21    <!--
2026-05-14T05:00:39.8795175Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-14T05:00:39.8795367Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-14T05:00:39.8795722Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-14T05:00:39.8796048Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-14T05:00:39.8796383Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-14T05:00:39.8796849Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-14T05:00:39.8797190Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-14T05:00:39.8797657Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-14T05:00:39.8797991Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-14T05:00:39.8798272Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-14T05:00:39.8798419Z 32    -->
2026-05-14T05:00:39.8798834Z 33    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
